(ABIGAIL PANTING)

01:02:41.750 --> 01:02:43.375
(FIREWORKS EXPLODING)

01:02:47.166 --> 01:02:48.291
(SIGHS)

01:02:50.041 --> 01:02:52.166
(YELLS) No! Wait! Stop!

01:02:52.166 --> 01:02:53.208
No!

01:03:01.333 --> 01:03:02.834
(PANTING)

01:03:04.875 --> 01:03:06.208
(GROANING)

01:03:13.000 --> 01:03:15.583
MAN ON RADIO:
Up, down, and all around.

01:03:15.583 --> 01:03:17.750
The most requested song
of this hour...

01:03:17.750 --> 01:03:19.333
(ENGINE REVS)

01:03:20.542 --> 01:03:23.333
It's 10 minutes before 3:00.
70 degrees.

01:03:23.333 --> 01:03:24.875
Please! Please, help me!

01:03:24.875 --> 01:03:28.208
We'll be playing the songs
you wanna hear,
all night long.

01:03:29.917 --> 01:03:31.250
(ABIGAIL SOBBING)

01:03:32.041 --> 01:03:33.750
(POP SONG PLAYING)

01:03:42.875 --> 01:03:43.917
Please.

01:03:48.667 --> 01:03:49.875
Please.

01:04:05.041 --> 01:04:07.041
You don't have to do this.

01:04:31.583 --> 01:04:33.792
(SHAKILY)
You don't have to do this.

01:04:42.333 --> 01:04:44.125
Please, don't do this.

01:05:00.291 --> 01:05:02.000
I'm already dead.

01:05:21.333 --> 01:05:22.917
Friday night in Los Angeles,

01:05:22.917 --> 01:05:26.208
a movie actress
and four of her friends
were murdered.

01:05:26.208 --> 01:05:28.375
And the circumstances
were lurid.

01:05:28.375 --> 01:05:31.166
REPORTER ON TV: The crime
scene resembled a strange,
religious ritual.

01:05:31.166 --> 01:05:33.208
A maid discovered
the bodies in the morning,

01:05:33.208 --> 01:05:35.000
and went screaming
for neighbors.

01:05:35.000 --> 01:05:38.583
A wandering band of members
of a so-called religious cult,

01:05:38.583 --> 01:05:40.792
with a leader they call Jesus,

01:05:40.792 --> 01:05:43.166
has had three
of its followers arrested.

01:05:43.166 --> 01:05:45.458
WOMAN ON TV:
Uh, we drove to the house

01:05:45.458 --> 01:05:49.709
with instructions
to kill everyone in the house.

01:05:49.709 --> 01:05:53.208
I felt absolutely
nothing for her
as she begged for her life.

01:05:53.208 --> 01:05:55.000
One of the people said,
"Who are you?"

01:05:55.000 --> 01:05:58.000
And Tex said,
"I'm the devil, and I'm here
to do the devil's business."

01:06:00.792 --> 01:06:02.250
MANSON: Believe me.

01:06:02.250 --> 01:06:04.333
If I started murdering people,

01:06:05.667 --> 01:06:07.583
there'd be none of you left.

01:06:10.291 --> 01:06:12.709
Because my children
are coming.
